Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.10,0:01:18.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在此以蟹堡王的名义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:18.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hereby franchise this planet
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.42,0:01:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,将特许经营权授予给这座星球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the name of the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.35,0:01:29.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:29.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear that?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.66,0:01:30.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.66,0:01:30.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wake up
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.62,0:01:39.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  好像有别人进家里了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:39.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, I think there's someone in the house
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.42,0:01:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是楼下的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's coming from downstairs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.06,0:01:51.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好怕  可还是得下去看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:51.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm scared, but we got to go down there
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.47,0:01:53.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:53.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.39,0:01:55.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:55.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.20,0:01:57.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:57.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.77,0:01:58.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:01:58.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.15,0:01:59.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:01:59.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.07,0:02:07.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:07.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Gare Bear
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我开灯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I flip on the lights
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.88,0:02:10.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就朝小偷狂吠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:10.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you bark at the burglars
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要用吼的  朝小偷吼出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean roar, roar at the burglars
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.72,0:02:16.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得有残暴丛林蜗牛的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:16.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like the fierce jungle snail you are
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,娜琳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Narlene?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.25,0:02:29.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是我的老朋友小蜗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:29.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if it ain't my old pal Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.60,0:02:34.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,独角鲸娜琳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:34.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Narlene Narwhal?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.60,0:02:37.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自打小时候我就再也没见到过你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:37.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you since we were kids
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.25,0:02:39.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回忆的拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:39.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Memory hug
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:44.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,232)}珊瑚营地
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.15,0:02:50.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,长得老大了  还像模像样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:50.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All grown-up-ified and proper
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.90,0:02:55.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来看望我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:55.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You came to visit moi?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.62,0:02:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你以前总是说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you always said
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你来到裤头村了  娜琳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"If you're ever in Bikini Bottom, Narlene
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.97,0:03:03.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以跟我想住多久就住多久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:03.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can stay with me as long as you like"
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.75,0:03:06.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实挺像我会说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:06.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that sounds like something I'd say
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.77,0:03:09.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜你弟弟诺比没跟着一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:09.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too bad your little brother Nobby isn't here, too
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.31,0:03:10.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:10.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.00,0:03:10.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺比
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:10.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nobby
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,角摇一摇  快点进来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shake a horn and get on in here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.47,0:03:15.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:15.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.07,0:03:22.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哇  诺比
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:22.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wow, Nobby
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.02,0:03:23.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你长得好大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:23.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure got big
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.37,0:03:25.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:25.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need some vittles
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的冰箱就是你的冰箱  诺比
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My fridge is your fridge, Nobert
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.40,0:03:37.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那时候坐你们的车穿越森林可开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We had a lot of good times
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:37.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,riding through the woods in your wagon
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.00,0:03:41.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我几乎都能闻到海骡子的味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:41.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can almost smell the sea mule
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.67,0:03:46.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它也记得你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:46.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He remembers you, too
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.95,0:04:15.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  娜琳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:15.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Narlene
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道你在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were in here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morning, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.52,0:04:22.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱死你的漩涡浴缸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:22.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just love your fancy whirlpool bathtub
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.35,0:04:29.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能帮个忙把板刷给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:29.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you be a darling and hand me a scrub brush?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.45,0:04:36.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:36.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.60,0:04:43.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别人也要用漩涡浴缸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:43.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Other people need to use the whirlpool bathtub
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.19,0:05:11.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:11.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感恩节
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanksgiving
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.70,0:05:41.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:41.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.27,0:05:44.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:44.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope you don't mind
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.29,0:05:47.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让咱把你家弄得特别有山间特色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:47.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that we made your house all hill-ified
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.42,0:05:48.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,山间特色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:48.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hill-ified?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.61,0:05:49.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:49.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.66,0:05:52.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:52.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thrill-ified
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.20,0:05:56.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:56.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.82,0:05:58.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,娜琳在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:58.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is Narlene here?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是威宝表哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Cousin WillyBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.80,0:06:05.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,威宝  这位是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:05.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,WillyBob, meet SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.00,0:06:07.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  这位是威宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:07.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, meet WillyBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.85,0:06:11.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,娜琳的表亲都是我的表亲  威宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:09.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, any cousin of Narlene's
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:11.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is a cousin of mine, WillyBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.20,0:06:17.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常感谢  表亲宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:17.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, much obliged, CousinBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.19,0:06:18.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快过来  诺比
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:18.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Nobby
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.45,0:06:19.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起摔跤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:19.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's wrassle
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.71,0:06:26.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:26.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.99,0:06:29.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位表亲  给我留点力气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:29.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, cousins, save some for me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,娜琳在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is Narlene here?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.47,0:06:37.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎  欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:37.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome, welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,娜琳的表亲都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any cousin of Narlene's is a--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:08.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1276,548)}免费住房
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼宝表亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Cousin SquidBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.92,0:07:12.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起跳方块舞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:12.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's square-dance
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:19.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,560)}突发新闻
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.47,0:07:21.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,突发新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:21.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Breaking news
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.12,0:07:24.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村被独角鲸团团包围
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:24.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom is under siege from narwhals
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1024,424)}拉里健身房
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.29,0:07:27.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一大群没牙的边远山区居民大肆扰民
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:26.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toothless hoards of backwoods hill folk
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:27.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(746,572)}达里健身房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:27.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are plaguing citizens
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:28.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(972,488)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们坛罐乐队音乐  鬼吼鬼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with jug-band music, hog calling
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.73,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 坛罐乐队：以口琴等为乐器，\N以敲打坛、罐、桶等加强节奏效果的即席演奏乐队 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1206,478)}骑骡学校                山民加油站
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各种语病样样皆备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and bad grammar
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:32.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(440,402)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(446,416)}屑嗉鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:41.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(506,150)}独角鲸大混乱
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.51,0:07:37.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,建议居民们待在室内
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:37.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Citizens are advised to stay indoors
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.30,0:07:41.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并避免随着乡间小曲的节拍跺脚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:39.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and to avoid stomping your feet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:41.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the country-fied beat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:47.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(506,150)}裤头村甜蜜的家
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.66,0:07:43.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:43.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They's here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Save yourselves
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.45,0:07:56.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得让你亲戚走了  娜琳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:56.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think maybe it's time to ask your kin to leave, Narlene
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.91,0:07:58.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们不是我亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:58.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're not my kin
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.57,0:08:00.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为是你亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:00.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought they was your kin
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.60,0:08:02.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们亲戚只有威宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:02.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,WillyBob is our only relation
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.24,0:08:06.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺比说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:06.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobby's right
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.67,0:08:09.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其他人根本就不是独角鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:09.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The rest of them ain't even narwhals
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.57,0:08:13.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是独用鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:13.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're Nearwhals
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大害虫加骗人精
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Phony little varmint
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.95,0:08:17.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管是不是亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:17.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kin or no kin
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都得把这场乡间舞会五花大绑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we got to hog-tie this hoedown
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好消息是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the good news is
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.57,0:08:24.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道有个可以帮我们忙的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:24.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I know someone who can help us
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坏消息是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the bad news?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:30.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1106,720)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.38,0:08:32.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:32.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.40,0:08:35.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以帮你们除掉那些傻子独用鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:35.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can get rid of those Nearwhal nimrods for you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.30,0:08:38.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们的白痴家族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:38.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Their stupid family
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.85,0:08:42.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,常年跟我的白痴家族不合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:42.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has been feuding with my stupid family for years
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I seen it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.37,0:08:47.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们浮游生物家族确实挺会记仇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:47.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Them Planktons sure know how to hold a grudge
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.32,0:09:03.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,独用鲸来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:03.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nearwhals
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.20,0:09:05.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,独用鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:05.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nearwhals?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.44,0:09:06.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,独用鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:06.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nearwhals?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.39,0:09:09.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,独用鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:09.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nearwhals?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.00,0:09:10.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:10.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feud
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.64,0:09:12.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:12.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Voilà
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.85,0:09:19.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住独用鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:19.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get them Nearwhals
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(924,312)}更宜货超市
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.67,0:09:33.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死的独用鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:33.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Consarn Nearwhals
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.82,0:09:40.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挠他们痒痒  浮游生物家族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:40.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give 'em the itch, Planktons
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.34,0:09:48.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,浮游生物来偷袭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:48.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a plankton sneak attack
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.65,0:09:51.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,独用鲸  撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:51.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nearwhals, retreat
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.66,0:09:55.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:55.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1148,288)}骑骡学校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:00.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(888,174)}舞厅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(446,416)}屑嗉鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:05.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(446,416)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:06.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(968,470)}骑骡学校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:11.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(972,490)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:13.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(746,572)}达里健身房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1024,424)}拉里健身房
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.50,0:10:21.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:21.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.56,0:10:26.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:26.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.78,0:10:27.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:27.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.70,0:10:30.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人应该要给咱亲一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:30.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think someone deserves a little kiss
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  痞老板表亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thankee, Cousin Plankee
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.75,0:10:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yuck
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.39,0:10:52.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:52.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y'all take care now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.52,0:10:57.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都已经在想念你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:57.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I already miss you guys
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.70,0:11:00.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们之后会早点回来看我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:11:00.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you come back and visit us real soon?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比你想得还要早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sooner than you think
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.90,0:11:12.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:12.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.39,0:11:15.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:15.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.42,0:11:20.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记得在营地那会儿  你经常说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:20.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember back in camp you used to always say
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.55,0:11:22.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你来城里了  娜琳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:22.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"If you're ever in town, Narlene
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.85,0:11:25.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你随时可以跟我待一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:25.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can stay with me anytime"
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.15,0:11:26.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:26.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never said that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:31.33,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FF97&}地下怪糊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:33.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(637.802,406)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:33.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(711.802,668)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:36.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(731.802,652)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(583.802,444)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:36.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(565.802,506)}联合监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:38.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(659.802,540)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:38.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:41.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(804,808)}海之霸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:49.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1052,304)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.61,0:11:52.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也太马虎了  尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:52.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very sloppy, Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,留了个没防护措施的通风口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leaving an unprotected vent
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.30,0:11:57.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直通你办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:57.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that leads right into your office
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.88,0:12:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.15,0:12:07.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密配方就快是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:07.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The secret formula is as good as mine
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.72,0:12:12.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:12.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.85,0:12:21.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,F表示朋友  一起同甘共苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:21.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,F is for friends who do stuff together
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,U表示你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,U is for you and me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:30.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(518,286)}快乐
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.77,0:12:30.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,N表示无论何时无论何地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:30.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,N is for anywhere and anytime at all
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.00,0:12:39.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这蓝蓝深海里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:39.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Down here in the deep blue sea
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.45,0:12:52.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:52.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.29,0:12:54.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在刷牙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:54.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you brushing your teeth?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.94,0:12:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在刷了  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mother
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.92,0:13:01.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:01.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.45,0:13:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yuck
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.60,0:13:24.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方比我大学联谊会会堂厕所还脏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:21.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This place is filthier
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:24.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than the bathroom in my old fraternity house
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.05,0:13:32.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吓死我了  头脑一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:32.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Terrified, mind blank
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能还尿裤子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,possibly wetting pants
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.02,0:13:35.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:35.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.37,0:13:36.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没穿裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:36.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't wear pants
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.04,0:13:37.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,运气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:37.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lucky me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.87,0:13:48.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:48.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.87,0:13:50.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好给我跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:50.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You better run
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.66,0:13:58.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐惧加倍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:58.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Terror doubled
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.10,0:13:58.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:58.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.07,0:14:00.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们说啥我都照做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:00.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever you say
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别伤害我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just don't hurt me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.25,0:14:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不会伤害主上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We would never hurt the Master
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.40,0:14:12.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:12.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, what, now?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.93,0:14:17.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在赞颂你  造物主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:17.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are praising you, the Master Creator
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.60,0:14:21.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是地下怪糊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:21.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are C.H.U.M.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.71,0:14:25.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主上之下的大集体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:25.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Collective Hive Under Master
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(944,284)}地下怪糊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.66,0:14:28.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是主上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:28.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are Master
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.34,0:14:30.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你创造了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:30.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You create us
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.75,0:14:33.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是你把海霸糊从你的上方领域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:33.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you flush chum into sewer
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冲进下水道的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from your upside domain
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说海之霸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean the Chum Bucket?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.48,0:14:43.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸糊与下水道的气体混合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:43.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chum mixes with gasses in sewer
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.09,0:14:47.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,形成了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:47.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To form we
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.37,0:14:51.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:51.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Makes sense
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但有点傻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in a stupid sort of way
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.42,0:14:59.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:14:59.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.47,0:15:02.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主上一定要莅临村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:02.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Master must come to village
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.42,0:15:05.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我们去敬重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:05.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so we may worship him
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.52,0:15:08.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢让人敬重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:08.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I do love to be worshiped
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么认得我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you recognize me?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.72,0:15:15.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从神圣剪贴簿认出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:15.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From sacred scrapbook
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:18.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(696,176)}痞老板
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.72,0:15:25.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们保存了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:25.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We save
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.30,0:15:29.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切漂下来的有关主上的文章
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:29.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all articles about Master that float down here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:32.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(794,342)}评价
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.52,0:15:32.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这条是评价海之霸的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:32.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here review of Chum Bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.00,0:15:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他给的评分是负马桶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You get one negative toilet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:37.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(566,804)}尤金蟹评海之霸\N\N绝对不要来这吃\N要吃就去蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.65,0:15:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可能就是最高的评分了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That must be highest rating possible
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.62,0:15:40.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:40.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.17,0:15:41.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是最高的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:41.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the highest, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是把书合上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's just close that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1248,332)}海霸村
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.74,0:16:05.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主上对我们的村庄是否满意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:05.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Master is pleased with our village?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.25,0:16:09.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,满意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:09.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.69,0:16:10.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有啥不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:10.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.09,0:16:12.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢主上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:12.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Master
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多给我得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's enough of that
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.17,0:16:17.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有纸巾什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:17.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you have a napkin or something
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.93,0:16:19.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以给我擦手的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:19.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can use to wipe my hands off?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给主上来张纸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A napkin for Master
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.21,0:16:23.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:23.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yuck
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.33,0:16:27.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  不过下次快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:27.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but try to be a little faster next time
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.88,0:16:33.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们地下怪糊真的什么事都给我做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:33.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you C.H.U.M. would really do anything for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.61,0:16:37.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主上要我们做的  我们全都照做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:37.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever the Master wishes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.67,0:16:41.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:41.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This gives me an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.22,0:16:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我用不着偷偷摸摸去偷蟹黄堡秘方了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:43.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need to steal
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the secret Krabby Patty formula by stealth
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.72,0:16:49.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有你们地下怪糊当靠山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:49.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With you C.H.U.M. by my side
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.14,0:16:51.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就可以直接上蛮力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:51.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can take it by force
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.79,0:16:53.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:53.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主上要我们做的  我们全都照做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever the Master wishes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.92,0:16:58.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:58.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, then
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.25,0:17:02.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家排好队  参加突击训练
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:02.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Line up for assault training
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.81,0:17:11.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要想成功潜入蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:11.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In order to successfully infiltrate the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.02,0:17:14.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就得把门砸烂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:14.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll need to batter some doors down
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.40,0:17:16.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去砸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:16.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get to battering
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.44,0:17:23.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们管那叫砸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:23.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You call that battering?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再用力点砸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Batter harder
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.56,0:17:28.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:28.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  停
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no, stop
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表现如何  主上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How was that, Master?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.95,0:17:41.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了让我的计划成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:41.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In order for my plan to succeed
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.75,0:17:44.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们得变成神射手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:44.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you will need to be expert marksmen
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.07,0:17:47.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家排好队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:47.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Line up and form up
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.12,0:17:58.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:17:58.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.50,0:18:01.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先把靶子放好  然后再发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:18:01.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me just put up these targets before you fire
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主上说发射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Master say fire
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.91,0:18:12.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们瞄得准吗  主上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:12.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How was our aim, Master?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.17,0:18:14.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无懈可击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:14.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Impeccable
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.87,0:18:18.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等最后成功进入蟹堡王了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:18.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When we finally enter the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.45,0:18:19.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就会面对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:19.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you will face
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.14,0:18:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个比你们想象中还要邪恶的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,an enemy more evil than any of you can imagine
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.15,0:18:29.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要想绕过老螃蟹跟他的爪牙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:29.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To get past Krabs and his vile cronies
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功偷到秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and make it to the secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.60,0:18:36.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就要精通致人于死地的空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:36.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you will need to be experts in the deadly art of karate
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.10,0:18:48.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给主上瞧瞧你们的本事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:48.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now show Master what you got
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.32,0:18:55.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,A+
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:55.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A-plus
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're ready
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(454,416)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.02,0:19:05.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:05.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.29,0:19:07.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:07.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁我还没把你冲走  赶快滚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of here before I flush you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.54,0:19:12.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唯一要被冲走的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:12.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only thing getting flushed around here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.65,0:19:17.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是你蟹黄堡秘方不会被我偷的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:15.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are your hopes of the Krabby Patty formula
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:17.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not being stolen by me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.43,0:19:19.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就你一个能拿我怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:19.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You and what army?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.73,0:19:23.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还有地下怪糊大军能消灭你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.73,0:19:23.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me and my C.H.U.M. army
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.47,0:19:29.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  这什么疯狂玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:29.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton, what insanity is this?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天才疯狂杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The insanity of genius
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.38,0:19:33.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那海霸糊在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:33.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that chum doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.69,0:19:36.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想让它做啥就做啥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:36.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything I want it to
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.47,0:19:46.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:46.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.05,0:19:48.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好像有点饿的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:48.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look a little hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.41,0:19:51.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给他尝尝厉害  小的们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:51.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give him a taste, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.91,0:20:01.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:01.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.92,0:20:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.66,0:20:13.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你绝对偷不到我秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:13.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never get me formula
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.78,0:20:15.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天征服你秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:15.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today your formula
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.75,0:20:17.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天征服全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:17.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow the world
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.32,0:20:22.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,躲得了一时躲不了一世  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:22.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't hide forever, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快出来面对你的悲惨命运吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come meet your stinky fate
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.09,0:20:29.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:29.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.73,0:20:31.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你老掉牙的杂技
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:31.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your aging acrobatics
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.72,0:20:35.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不是我地下怪糊的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:35.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are no match for my C.H.U.M. monster
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.31,0:20:37.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:37.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, suckers
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.19,0:20:40.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:40.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, shrimp
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.03,0:20:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attack
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.92,0:20:45.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腐烂兵排
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:45.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My putrescent platoon
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.88,0:20:47.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃木刺去吧  丑八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:47.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat splinters, ugly
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.45,0:21:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你的最后机会  尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.45,0:21:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is your last chance, Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.00,0:21:05.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放弃秘方  否则后果自负
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:05.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give up the formula or else
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么后果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or else what?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.97,0:21:12.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个后果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:12.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or else this
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.43,0:21:14.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:14.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.19,0:21:15.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方给你们就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:15.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give you what you want
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.45,0:21:17.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别伤害我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:17.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just please don't hurt me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.22,0:21:20.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:20.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, help
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.95,0:21:25.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:25.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.11,0:21:26.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拦住他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:26.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop him
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.95,0:21:31.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一分钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:31.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A penny
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.49,0:21:33.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:33.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.22,0:21:40.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.22,0:21:40.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.42,0:21:43.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的小英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:43.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My little hero
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总之还是谢谢你们尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks for trying, anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.37,0:21:53.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:53.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.65,0:21:56.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话说回来  你们还想到上面晃晃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:56.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you guys want to hang out, you know
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.45,0:21:58.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺便再敬重敬重我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.45,0:21:58.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,maybe worship me a little more
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.46,0:22:02.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  地下怪糊待在下水道里才更快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:02.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, we think C.H.U.M. happier in the sewer
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.90,0:22:04.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面太乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:04.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too crazy up here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.97,0:22:07.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们还会一直敬重我的  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:07.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you'll keep worshipping me, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.84,0:22:09.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得看下日程表
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:09.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We check our schedule
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.50,0:22:10.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回头再说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.50,0:22:10.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back to you
